metadata.name: Pure #1
metadata.description:
Pure #1 

The first picture from this collection. Pure is a collaboration project with my beautiful model Jana. It's limited to 10 pieces which are minted one after the other. 

If desired, the first collector of this picture may claim a signed DIN A5 fineart print. An additional signature by the model is also possible.

4480x6272px // 300 dpi // 10,9 MB
